<view class="page data-v-2e97051e"><view class="status-card data-v-2e97051e"><view class="status-head data-v-2e97051e"><text class="status-title data-v-2e97051e">当前认证状态</text><text class="status-tag data-v-2e97051e">{{a}}</text></view><text class="status-tip data-v-2e97051e">{{b}}</text></view><view class="section-card data-v-2e97051e"><view class="section-head data-v-2e97051e"><text class="section-title data-v-2e97051e">实名信息</text><text class="section-desc data-v-2e97051e">请填写与证件一致的真实身份信息，便于平台审核。</text></view><view class="form-item data-v-2e97051e"><text class="label data-v-2e97051e">真实姓名</text><input class="input data-v-2e97051e" placeholder="请输入真实姓名" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" value="{{c}}" bindinput="{{d}}"/></view><view class="form-item no-border data-v-2e97051e"><text class="label data-v-2e97051e">身份证号</text><input class="input data-v-2e97051e" placeholder="请输入身份证号" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" value="{{e}}" bindinput="{{f}}"/></view></view><view class="section-card data-v-2e97051e"><view class="section-head data-v-2e97051e"><text class="section-title data-v-2e97051e">证书照片</text><text class="section-desc data-v-2e97051e">优先上传清晰、完整、无遮挡的证书照片，审核会更顺畅。</text></view><view wx:for="{{g}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="f" class="upload-item data-v-2e97051e"><text class="label data-v-2e97051e">{{item.a}}</text><view class="upload-box data-v-2e97051e" bindtap="{{item.e}}"><image wx:if="{{item.b}}" class="upload-image data-v-2e97051e" src="{{item.c}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view wx:else class="upload-placeholder data-v-2e97051e"><text class="upload-placeholder-text data-v-2e97051e">{{item.d}}</text></view></view></view></view><view class="bottom-bar data-v-2e97051e"><button class="submit-btn data-v-2e97051e" loading="{{h}}" disabled="{{i}}" bindtap="{{j}}"> 提交认证资料 </button></view></view>